               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. HILL</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined.</hi> This watch-movement last produced, is mine, and part of the property I lost.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I left, to obtain better employment; the street-door was very often left open; any one could walk in and take them; there was a lodger in the house named Bannister, who Mr. Hill told me he thought was a bad character.</p>
